product_intent: Create an e-commerce website for selling handmade jewelry online.
target_user: Customers looking to purchase handmade jewelry.
core_features: Shopping cart functionality (adding items to a virtual cart)
Secure payment processing (making online payments for purchases)
technical_constraints: Database for products and user carts
